<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="28" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1436,1304,1511]" box="[151,558,1304,1331]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,530,1304,1331]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
5.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1436,1304,1511]" box="[199,1067,1340,1367]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1340,1367]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Distribution.</emphasis>
Europe, except for the south. 
<collectingCountry box="[690,789,1341,1367]" name="Portugal" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: two northern provinces.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1436,1304,1511]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1377,1403]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Ecology.</emphasis>
Collected in 
<collectingCountry box="[455,550,1377,1403]" name="Portugal" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Portugal</collectingCountry>
in two riparian habitats, one of which was situated in mountainous heathland with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Jussieu" authorityYear="1789" box="[208,321,1413,1439]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ericaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Ericaceae</taxonomicName>
. In 
<collectingCountry box="[361,460,1413,1439]" name="Belgium" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Belgium</collectingCountry>
, this species is also confined to humid heathlands (
<bibRefCitation author="Pollet, M." box="[1031,1166,1413,1439]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref34362" refString="Pollet, M. (2000) A documented Red List of the dolichopodid flies (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) of Flanders [in Dutch with English summary]. Communications of the Institute of Nature Conservation, 8, 1 - 190." type="journal article" year="2000">Pollet 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1436,1304,1511]" box="[199,646,1448,1475]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,1448,1475]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
2.3 (rare). Fairly rare (FL).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1436,1304,1511]" box="[199,584,1484,1511]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,1484,1511]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Activity period.</emphasis>
